&lt;p data-start=&quot;256&quot; data-end=&quot;501&quot;&gt;At &lt;strong data-start=&quot;259&quot; data-end=&quot;268&quot;&gt;eLEND&lt;/strong&gt;, we’re always looking for passionate, driven, and talented individuals who want to make an impact in the mortgage industry. Even if you don’t see a role posted that fits your background right now, we’d still love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;503&quot; data-end=&quot;676&quot;&gt;By joining our &lt;strong data-start=&quot;518&quot; data-end=&quot;538&quot;&gt;Talent Community&lt;/strong&gt;, you’ll stay connected with eLEND and be among the first to know when new opportunities open that align with your skills and interests.&lt;/p&gt;
