&lt;li data-start=&quot;1095&quot; data-end=&quot;1133&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1097&quot; data-end=&quot;1133&quot;&gt;Motivated and relationship-driven.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1134&quot; data-end=&quot;1197&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1136&quot; data-end=&quot;1197&quot;&gt;Passionate about creating an excellent borrower experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1198&quot; data-end=&quot;1251&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1200&quot; data-end=&quot;1251&quot;&gt;Eager to grow in a fast-paced, evolving industry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1252&quot; data-end=&quot;1317&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1254&quot; data-end=&quot;1317&quot;&gt;Open to new challenges and opportunities in mortgage lending.&lt;/p&gt;
