&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;🚀 About Us&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;At eLEND, we’re transforming the lending industry through technology, automation, artificial intelligence, and modern digital platforms. By combining deep financial services expertise with innovative technology solutions, we create scalable products that enhance operational efficiency, improve customer experiences, and drive business performance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;As we continue to modernize and scale our technology ecosystem, we are seeking a Senior Technical Product Manager to join our Alpha Team and help drive strategic product and technology initiatives across the enterprise.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;✨ Why This Role Matters&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;The Senior Technical Product Manager serves as the critical connection point between business stakeholders, product leadership, engineering, architecture, data, operations, and executive leadership.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;This role is instrumental in translating strategic business objectives into scalable technology solutions while ensuring delivery excellence, architectural integrity, and operational alignment. You will lead requirements gathering, technical documentation, delivery coordination, and innovation initiatives while helping shape the future of AI-enabled products, automation, and digital transformation across the organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;🛠️ Key Responsibilities&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;Product Management &amp;amp; Strategy&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;• Partner with business stakeholders to gather, analyze, and document business and technical requirements.&lt;br&gt;• Translate business objectives into epics, user stories, acceptance criteria, and functional specifications.&lt;br&gt;• Own and maintain product backlogs aligned with strategic priorities.&lt;br&gt;• Support product discovery, roadmap development, feature prioritization, and solution design.&lt;br&gt;• Ensure alignment between business goals, customer needs, and technical implementation strategies.&lt;br&gt;• Drive accountability, transparency, and traceability throughout the product lifecycle.&lt;br&gt;• Collaborate with leadership to support enterprise-wide product and innovation initiatives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;Technical Documentation &amp;amp; Architecture&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;• Establish documentation standards, governance processes, and best practices across product and technology teams.&lt;br&gt;• Create and maintain:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Product Requirement Documents (PRDs)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Functional Specifications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technical Design Documents&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Process Flows and Business Workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;API Documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Integration Specifications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Architecture Decision Records (ADRs)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operational Runbooks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Release Notes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;User Acceptance Testing Documentation&lt;br&gt;• Develop and maintain architecture, workflow, sequence, integration, and data flow diagrams.&lt;br&gt;• Create and manage:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;System Architecture Diagrams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Application Interaction Diagrams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data Flow Diagrams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Entity Relationship Diagrams (ERDs)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;User Journey Maps&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Business Process Models&lt;br&gt;• Ensure documentation remains synchronized with evolving systems, integrations, AI solutions, and platform architectures.&lt;br&gt;• Champion Documentation-as-Code methodologies using Markdown, Mermaid, Git-based repositories, and modern knowledge management tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;🚀 About Us&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;At eLEND, we’re transforming the lending industry through technology, automation, artificial intelligence, and modern digital platforms. We combine deep financial services expertise with cutting-edge innovation to build scalable solutions that improve operational efficiency, customer experience, and business performance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;As part of our modernization journey, we are seeking a &lt;strong&gt;Technical Product Manager&lt;/strong&gt; – Enterprise &amp;amp; Cross-Functional Initiatives to drive strategic programs that span Product, Technology, Operations, Data, and Innovation. This role is ideal for a leader who thrives at the intersection of business strategy, enterprise transformation, AI, and technology execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;✨ Why This Role Matters&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;Technical Product Manager&lt;/strong&gt; serves as a strategic connector across the organization, helping align business priorities, technology investments, operational objectives, and innovation initiatives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;This role is responsible for driving enterprise-wide initiatives, improving organizational alignment, maintaining architectural and process transparency, and supporting modernization efforts through strong documentation, governance, and execution practices. You will work directly with executive leadership and cross-functional teams to help shape the future operating model of a modern AI-enabled FinTech organization.&lt;/p&gt;
